metadata.name: Dormiveglia
metadata.description:
Only one of the many areas where life is felt and awareness is experienced is the "pole". This area where the soul is liberated and the mind calms is the starting point of every new existence. The game continues despite everything, the token of this game is awareness, you can buy it just by staying in the moment. Each awakening opens onto the scene of a new story, this scene is neither past nor future, this scene is that "moment". It is dedicated to the "moment". Surrender is the light of the stage. It is the moment when we say yes to the existence of life. The present moment is as it always is. Can you let this happen?

dormiveglia: the space that stretches between sleeping and waking

8-bit narrative dedicated to Zey and to the "moment" of its existence
